iting it inspired.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 29. Jul 2022) 0aAngels in art. 0aExpressionism (Art)zGermanyy20th century. 0aJewish art and symbolismzGermanyy20th century. 0aUnderdrawing. 7aART / General.2bisacsh  aR. H. Quaytman, Paul Klee, Walter Benjamin, Martin Luther, German-Jewish, Angelus Novus, First World War.08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE Architecture and Design 2022z9783110992793oZDB-23-DAD08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE Arts, Architecture and Design 2022 Englishz978311099281608iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE COMPLETE 2022 Englishz978311099389908iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE COMPLETE 2022z9783110994810oZDB-23-DGG08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertUniversity of Chicago Complete eBook-Package 2022z978311076650940uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9780226816715423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9780226816715/original  a978-3-11-076650-9  University of Chicago Complete eBook-Package 2022b2022  a978-3-11-099281-6  EBOOK PACKAGE Arts, Architecture and Design 2022 Englishb2022  a978-3-11-099389-9  EBOOK PACKAGE COMPLETE 2022 Englishb2022  aGBV-deGruyter-alles  aZDB-23-DADb2022  aZDB-23-DGGb2022